{"tid":48679,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"［有圖慎入］鬼片黎講不速之嚇算唔算世界級","createTime":"2016-12-21T08:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T18:57:28.000Z","uid":26682,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9068e4616e0d139e38d7d33f8ca71d8bcbe43a1c","tid":48679,"uid":26682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:11:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6A80vfX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6A80vfX.jpg&h=0e131d90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然唔算太恐怖 但劇情真係世界級<br />\n<br />\n好少睇Nicole Kidman嘅戲 但估唔到演技咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其他鬼片午夜凶鈴、鬼水凶鈴都唔駛多講<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1wR5T8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1wR5T8o.jpg&h=0140bee4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q33nP1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq33nP1e.jpg&h=e12dc2c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港代表我自己覺得<blockquote>大頭怪嬰</blockquote>故事比較完整同真係幾恐怖尤其係第二個結局 至今只係睇過一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/21/160413_3ae6123f36ec1747e1238c127dd4bd51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F21%2F160413_3ae6123f36ec1747e1238c127dd4bd51.jpg&h=ede3f40b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自己拉去最尾岀字幕個度<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/d0SAIoTrS18\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fd0SAIoTrS18&d=hJWVbOOBUG1PRdmMe5Ar%2BoscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=d684a580\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/d0SAIoTrS18</a><br />\n之後就係見鬼同熱血青年<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c41n70z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc41n70z.jpg&h=76628a0d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w9191g2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw9191g2.jpg&h=fe801403&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外有套外國嘅唔岀名，以巫術為題材<br />\n故事嘅女主角最後被個巫婆轉身成功，但可惜唔記得咩名，係少有邪個一方贏左<br />\n<br />\n大家有冇咩推介？"},{"pid":"76dc6de57de8c90a375524481114d3ab32093b84","tid":48679,"uid":18320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:12:05.000Z","msg":"屌你老母留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da89da3526bcb2afc48e23e14445b848539e82ce","tid":48679,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:13:18.000Z","msg":"日本點少得咒怨<br />\n白老婦黑少女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b95043df3531c779d1c4d65ac813e7f1bfe499c","tid":48679,"uid":26682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:38:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8k0OoW2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8k0OoW2.jpg&h=84a577c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來叫Skeleton Key <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e8dd156cb1e1cb9af81691f93297c1fc38c5167","tid":48679,"uid":55505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:40:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本點少得咒怨<br />\n白老婦黑少女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咒怨搞到我唔敢搭有窗既𨋢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04fae6ad42c64e76766af025b2df787a5dbc209b","tid":48679,"uid":60588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:45:00.000Z","msg":"The Orphanage <br />\n呢套都世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好少咁好睇既鬼片"},{"pid":"470cbc793eae69d7914b528774493394e156d451","tid":48679,"uid":944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:44:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8k0OoW2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbna